<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ur" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Maktab Minhaj Learning Academy</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            /* Background Image Implementation */
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)), 
                        url('https://i.ibb.co/C3fKzY6/MMLA-Logo.png');
            background-size: contain;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-position: center;
            color: #1b4332;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #084c31;
            color: #ffd700;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #ffd700;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo-img {
            width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid #ffd700;
            background: white;
            padding: 5px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            background: #0b5e3c;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .content-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-right: 8px solid #084c31;
        }

        h2 { color: #084c31; border-bottom: 2px solid #ffd700; padding-bottom: 10px; }

        .lang-section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .lang-ur { font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 2; text-align: right; }
        .lang-hi { font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; text-align: left; direction: ltr; color: #333; }
        .lang-en { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; text-align: left; direction: ltr; font-style: italic; color: #555; }

        .qr-section {
            text-align: center;
            background: #f0fdf4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px dashed #084c31;
        }

        .qr-img {
            width: 250px;
            max-width: 100%;
            border: 5px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .admission-btn {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #c91818;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .admission-btn:hover { background: #961212; transform: scale(1.05); }

        .policy-box {
            background: #fff5f5;
            border: 1px solid #feb2b2;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        footer {
            background: #084c31;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .whatsapp-float {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: #25d366;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            z-index: 1000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <img src="https://i.ibb.co/C3fKzY6/MMLA-Logo.png" alt="MMLA Logo" class="logo-img">
    <h1>مکتب منہاج لرننگ اکیڈمی</h1>
    <p>Educating Heart and Mind</p>
</header>

<div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#home">ہوم</a>
    <a href="#admission">داخلہ</a>
    <a href="#rules">قوانین</a>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="content-card" id="home">
        <div class="lang-section lang-ur">
            مکتب منہاج لرننگ اکیڈمی میں آپ کا خیر مقدم ہے۔ ہمارا مقصد دینی اور عصری تعلیم کے ذریعے نئی نسل کی بہترین تربیت کرنا ہے۔
        </div>
        <div class="lang-section lang-hi">
            मकतब मिन्हाज लर्निंग एकेडमी में आपका स्वागत है। हमारा उद्देश्य धार्मिक और आधुनिक शिक्षा के माध्यम से नई पीढ़ी को शिक्षित करना है।
        </div>
        <div class="lang-section lang-en">
            Welcome to Maktab Minhaj Learning Academy. Our mission is to provide quality religious and modern education.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card" id="admission">
        <h2>داخلہ اور فیس (Admission & Payment)</h2>
        <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd7DVMDHUEyy6YVwriZXhUbaoUXxrJDBJ3ZATJRIzZDeFGpwg/viewform" class="admission-btn">FILL ADMISSION FORM</a>
        
        <div class="qr-section">
            <h3>Scan to Pay Admission Fee</h3>
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/IMG-20260303-WA0091.jpg" alt="Payment QR" class="qr-img">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card" id="rules">
        <h2>📜 Terms & Privacy Policy</h2>
        <div class="policy-box">
            <p><strong>• Refund:</strong> Admission fees non-refundable hain. (داخلہ فیس واپس نہیں ہوگی)</p>
            <p><strong>• Discount:</strong> Gareeb aur Yateem bacchon ke liye vishesh chhoot aur muft taleem. (یتیم اور مستحق طلباء کے لیے خصوصی رعایت)</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<a href="https://wa.me/917667720172" class="whatsapp-float">Chat on WhatsApp</a>

<footer>
    <p>📞 Helpline: +91 76677 20172</p>
    <p>📍 Samastipur, Bihar</p>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Maktab Minhaj Learning Academy</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
